t;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/7feb62e138454879a559c873fec96164\" img_width=\"498\" img_height=\"368\" alt=\"詹姆斯的车A级，罗斯S级，唯独他的豪车SSS级+就差坦克了\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而这一位，他的坐骑算是NBA里面最贵的一辆了，他就是我们的罗斯，他的坐骑布加迪威龙在国内2500万以上，这辆车的引擎是W16，据说最快可达1000的马力，有10个散热器跟4个涡轮增压。买一辆这样的车，不知道罗斯有多有钱啊！如何忍心买这么贵的车啊，有钱人就这点追求吗？有钱人的世界是我们想象不到的。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/795ee2ea5aef4362a0d9ad3e0ac3603f\" img_width=\"486\" img_height=\"320\" alt=\"詹姆斯的车A级，罗斯S级，唯独他的豪车SSS级+就差坦克了\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而我吗最后一位，他的每的虽然没有罗斯的那么昂贵，但是他的车多到可以开一个小型的车展了，那就是大鲨鱼奥尼尔。他拥有40多辆车，什么劳斯莱斯、奔驰、法拉利、福特大皮卡等等各种豪车都有，连三轮的跑车都有，可能就差坦克了吧。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/901d83b530a64079a163bf6dcc4a833c\" img_width=\"554\" img_height=\"351\" alt=\"詹姆斯的车A级，罗斯S级，唯独他的豪车SSS级+就差坦克了\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每一辆都是价值不菲，真不知道他每天出门会不会犹豫很久今天到底应该开那一辆车出门，让我们这些普通轿车都买不起的人情何以堪。而且奥尼尔体积有那么大，很多车都是定制版的豪车。这位才是真正的豪啊！看得我是连声卧槽，当然联盟还有很多巨星的豪车，像魔兽霍华德的车就像装甲车一样刀枪不入。我啥时候要是有一辆也完美了。</p><p><br/></p>','0','0','0','0','0','0','  詹姆斯的车A级，罗斯S级，唯独他的豪车SSS级+就差坦克了','0');
INSERT INTO `qb_cms_content1` VALUES ('56','1','12','40多年前的法拉利，造型看上去还真特别……','1','1','3','1','0','0','1548326199','0','1548326199','uploads/images/20190124/1_20190124183629def61.jpeg','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图中这辆法拉利到现在已经有40多年的历史了！经过法拉利工程师修复！现已恢复原来的模样</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/20ea7dab15fb488aa130296e7409767c\" img_width=\"600\" img_height=\"348\" alt=\"40多年前的法拉利，造型看上去还真特别……\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为是定制版本，据说世界上只有三台，所以深受收藏家的追捧。这辆法拉利在最近的一次拍卖中以200万英镑的价格被一位藏家拍走，约和人民币1758万元人民币</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/745b1a2e6e5a4384b1609c404f803f7a\" img_width=\"600\" img_height=\"377\" alt=\"40多年前的法拉利，造型看上去还真特别……\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">后车厢看上去很大很特别。顶部有两块弧形的巨大玻璃天窗，这种弧形的天窗，即使是放在现在也没有几个汽车厂商敢这么干！在当时也算是大胆前卫的设</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/c9767c0512a04ad0b577c02bef83ad42\" img_width=\"600\