INSERT INTO `qb_cms_content1` VALUES ('58','1','12','红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！','1','1','12','1','0','0','1548326792','1550557852','1548326792','uploads/images/20190124/1_2019012418461955fea.jpeg','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为国产品牌的创始者，红旗一直在努力的创造有价值的车，不断地创新不断地研发，一直在努力着。那么下面就让我们来看看成果到底是会让人满意，还是会失望？</span></span></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/a392ae11ab364905be44da4486ea6048\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" alt=\"红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新车便是红旗L4，没错是国宾车红旗L5的小弟。一提到红旗L5，相信很多人都知道，这个车就是给国家领导人坐的车，整车也是舒适性和安全性都是很棒。那么作为小弟的红旗L4会有什么表现呢？</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/05c491a36ff84849abf3ee82b14e2ba3\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" alt=\"红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新车前脸几乎和老大哥红旗L5差不多的设计，只是在头灯方面有所改变，将圆形的头灯改换为长方形的头灯，并且雾灯也集成在了头灯里面。和L5一样，竖线型的中网也是颇具威武，下方的镀铬装饰，也时刻提醒着这是一辆红旗L4。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/429d1bac89554c448d525f68ca5e1f05\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" alt=\"红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">车身侧面，由于车型定位D级车之上，所以车身尺寸达到了5米3，轴距也是突破3米，可以说车内空间非常的宽敞。并且采用劳斯莱斯式的对开门设计，极具豪华感，侧身腰线也是十分的立体，并且轮毂的设计也是让车看起来十分的成熟。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/53532381e165414794b7168bccc705fb\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" alt=\"红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尾灯则采用长方形设计，中间带有镀铬饰条，让车尾看起来有劳斯莱斯幻影版的韵味，并且后备箱的空间也是十分的大，这都是应该属于这个级别应该有的东西。从后面看车尾，给人一种十足的高级感。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/c900d88a647740c096d8084cc4991951\" img_width=\"500\" img_height=\"330\" alt=\"红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">内饰方面，设计十分的简约，一颗硕大的多媒体屏幕，两侧也是用皮革和实木进行点缀，看起来也是十分的豪华，虽不及奔驰宝马奥迪的科技感，但也是将中国的独特文化展现在车中。在讲究科技的今天，红旗L4的独特设计无疑是一个新生。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为国产品牌的红旗，虽然起步较晚，但是一直在努力，一直在创造，此款车型也是十分出色，奔驰S宝马7系不可同它相比较。</p><p><br/></p>','0','0','0','0','0','0','红旗砸百亿造车，D级车或重新洗牌，气势秒杀奔驰宝马奥迪！','0');
INSERT INTO `qb_cms_content1` VALUES ('59','1','11','勇士有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪，伊戈和利文斯顿将成为牺牲品','1','1','20','1','0','0','1548327233','0','1548327233','uploads/images/20190124/1_20190124185344ae512.jpeg','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在NBA人情味是少见的，科比和诺维斯基应该是非常幸运的球员，勇士首发分卫克莱-汤普森的合同在2019年休赛期彻底到期，这位三冠核心的价值无以言表，他配上的顶薪续约。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/859b11da9a044569a11aa6e45769185e\" img_width=\"662\" img_height=\"826\" alt=\"勇士有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪，伊戈和利文斯顿将成为牺牲品\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">汤普森的合同可能会引起勇士阵容的大洗牌，勇士跟队记者斯特林透露：勇士管理层有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪合同，新合同会超过1.6亿美元，为此伊戈和利文斯顿将成为球队牺牲品。这样看来，勇士并不想在四-五年内离开争冠队列，保留了库里和汤普森，是勇士体系持续的保证。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">勇士给出这样的诚意，汤普森拒绝的可能性微乎及微。因为从整个阵容框架来说，库里、杜兰特甚至格林都是五年顶薪起步，连续拿下两年常规赛MVP的库里拿下顶薪无可厚非，连续两年拿到总决赛MVP的杜兰特顶薪续约势在必行，这时候能够给到汤普森顶薪续约，已经是勇士最大的努力了。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/c67656a8ac614a10a9d4d415f299588e\" img_width=\"666\" img_height=\"854\" alt=\"勇士有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪，伊戈和利文斯顿将成为牺牲品\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">汤普森在采访直言：我没考虑过会离开勇士，我一直在追求五年合同，不排除为勇士降薪的可能。要知道汤普森在新秀赛季开始一直在勇士效力，他完全可以要求勇士起薪3500万的续约合同，3200万起薪是他留下勇士做出的努力。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过勇士放弃伊戈达拉和利文斯顿还是让人很难以接受，在连续四年总决赛，这两位老将拿出了他们能够帮助勇士的所有东西，尤其是伊戈达拉在2015-2016赛季领防詹姆斯的场景历历在目，2015年的FMVP就是最好的证明。伊戈达拉34岁，利文斯顿33岁，年龄的增长让他们这个赛季战力大减，场均不足6分且薪资高达1600万美元，这是勇士必须要做的抉择。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/5d09ca8b362547fa8859f6082d901d9f\" img_width=\"1000\" img_height=\"746\" alt=\"勇士有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪，伊戈和利文斯顿将成为牺牲品\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">保留了库里、杜兰特和汤普森的勇士阵容，替补阵容将会变得非常廉价，这不是一个好的信号，但这意味着球队上限很高。</p><p><br/></p>','0','0','0','0','0','0','勇士有意匹配汤普森3200万起薪，伊戈和利文斯顿将成为牺牲品','0');
